snippet.title: Guardians Of Hyelore [PC] Trailer
snippet.description:
Guardians Of Hyelore is a the tug-of-war fantasy battler pitting your units and strategies against an onslaught of enemies.


More details here: https://worthplaying.com/game/15634-guardians-of-hyelore/


Guardians Of Hyelore (previously called Tower Rush) is coming to PC (Steam and Epic Games Store) on Sept. 29, 2021 for $19.99.
